Cyber Claw:






Cyber Claw screamed in a shrill voice as the other raptor grabbed her by the 
neck. A dirty move, but effective. This one is good. She tossed her head, 
screeching loudly, her voice getting deeper with her rage. She was famous 
for her voice and her temper. She threw herself on her back, landing on the 
other raptor.

She leaped up to her feet, and scurried backwards, into clearer view. She 
was almost identical to Dinobot, except she had dark skin under her eyes, 
due to her stresses of struggling to survive out in the wilds. She lowered 
her head, twitching her tail wildly. She flexed her inner toe claws.

"Get out!" she screamed at the other raptor. Her voice had turned into her 
Dinobot tone that was known to scare off rivals that knew him. "Get out!"

Suddenly, Cyber Claw could smell a new scent. She curled her lips, eyeing 
everything that could be seen.
